---

// Fundations
import Text from "@/components/fundations/elements/Text.astro";
import Wrapper from "@/components/fundations/containers/Wrapper.astro";
---

<section>
  <Wrapper variant="standard" class="pb-12">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <Text
        tag="h2"
        variant="displaySM"
        class="text-accent-950 uppercase font-display font-medium"
      >
        Everything you need to build fast, modern websites with Astro
      </Text>

      <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-500 mt-12">
        Astro helps you build ultra-fast websites with zero JavaScript by
        default making performance the default, not an afterthought. Whether
        you're just starting out or migrating from another stack, the learning
        curve is gentle and the tooling is refreshingly simple.
        <br /><br />
        You get full freedom to work with your favorite frameworks — React, Vue,
        Svelte, Solid — all in the same project. Combine them effortlessly while
        keeping your pages fast and clean. Write content in Markdown or MDX and
        enhance it with interactive components only where you need them.
        <br /><br />
        Want to connect to a headless CMS or fetch data from an API? Astro lets
        you do it at build time or runtime, with full control. When it's time to
        go live, deploy seamlessly to Netlify, Vercel, or your own infrastructure
        — optimized and ready.
        <br /><br />
        From performance-focused builds to smooth developer workflows, Astro keeps
        things productive. Enjoy fast reloads, great error messages, and a polished
        experience from start to ship — so you can launch confidently and showcase
        your work with pride.
      </Text>
     
    </div>
  </Wrapper>
</section>
